<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <title>MasterMind</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Mastermind</h1>
    <p class="intro">Introduction</p>
    <div class="introduction">
      <p class="small">In this game, the computer will generate a secret code with four letter from six letters. </p>
      <p class="small">The colors could be duplicated. And you have 12 chances to decode.</p>
      <p class="small">After each guess, the computer will give the answer upon how well the guess is.</p>

      <p class="small">"+": both color and position is correct</p>
      <p class="small">"-": only color is correct, and position is wrong</p>
    </div>

    <div class="table">
      <% if $pick != [] %>
        <table align="center">
          <tr>
            <td class="number">No.</td>
            <td> 1 </td>
            <td> 2 </td>
            <td> 3 </td>
            <td> 4 </td>
            <td class="answer"> Answer</td>
          </tr>
        <% data.each do |row|%>
          <tr>
            <td class="number"><%= row[0] %></td>
            <td><%= row[1] %></td>
            <td><%= row[2] %></td>
            <td><%= row[3] %></td>
            <td><%= row[4] %></td>
            <td class="answer"><%= row[5] %></td>
          </tr>
          <% end %>
        </table>
        <% end %>
    </div>


    <form method="POST" action="/index">

      <select class="" name="first">
        <option value="R">Red</option>
        <option value="B">Blue</option>
        <option value="Y">Yellow</option>
        <option value="P">Purple</option>
        <option value="G">Grey</option>
        <option value="T">Turquoise</option>
      </select>

      <select class=""  name="second">
        <option value="R">Red</option>
        <option value="B">Blue</option>
        <option value="Y">Yellow</option>
        <option value="P">Purple</option>
        <option value="G">Grey</option>
        <option value="T">Turquoise</option>
      </select>

      <select class="" name="third">
        <option value="R">Red</option>
        <option value="B">Blue</option>
        <option value="Y">Yellow</option>
        <option value="P">Purple</option>
        <option value="G">Grey</option>
        <option value="T">Turquoise</option>
      </select>

      <select class=""  name="fourth">
        <option value="R">Red</option>
        <option value="B">Blue</option>
        <option value="Y">Yellow</option>
        <option value="P">Purple</option>
        <option value="G">Grey</option>
        <option value="T">Turquoise</option>
      </select>

      <input class="buttom" type="submit" value="Guess!">
    </form>
    <p class="message"><%= message %></p>

  </body>
</html>
